COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 508, L.D. 1219
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, replaces the bill and
33 changes the title. The amendment provides ongoing funds to support a 4% increase in
44 funding to the University of Maine System in fiscal years 2025-26 and 2026-27. The
55 amendment removes the emergency preamble and emergency clause.
